# ✨ BlogSphere

A full-stack MERN blogging platform with authentication and comments.

## Live Demo

Frontend:
YOUR_VERCEL_LINK

Backend:
https://blog-platform-pql9.onrender.com

## Features

- User Authentication
- JWT Authorization
- Create/Edit/Delete Posts
- Comment System
- Search Functionality
- Responsive UI
- Dark Mode
- Dashboard
- Protected Routes

## Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React
- React Router
- Axios

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT

## Installation

### Backend

cd server

npm install

npm run dev

### Frontend

cd client

npm install

npm run dev

